(189, 1, '2017-05-09 06:46:38', '2017-05-09 06:46:38', 'You use Nexmo''s Shared Short Code APIs for:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href="https://docs.nexmo.com/messaging/us-short-codes-api/two-factor-authentication">Two-factor Authentication</a> - prove a user''s identity. Provision a US Short Code with a standard or custom template that specifies the custom parameters for two-factor authentication (2FA) messages.</li>\r\n 	<li><a href="https://docs.nexmo.com/messaging/us-short-codes-api/event-based-alerts">Event Based Alerts</a> - communicate with people using Event Based Alerts. Provision a US Short Code with a standard or custom template that specifies the custom parameters for Alert messages.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThese APIs support messaging to the US and Canada.\r\n\r\nFor more information about US Short Codes, see <a href="https://help.nexmo.com/hc/en-us/sections/200621203-Using-Pre-approved-U-S-Short-Codes%20target%20:%20_blank">help.nexmo.com/hc/en-us/sections/200621203-Using-Pre-approved-U-S-Short-Codes</a>.', 'US Short Codes API', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'us-short-codes-api', '', '', '2017-05-09 06:46:38', '2017-05-09 06:46:38', '', 175, 'http://localhost:8080/Nexmo/Source/BE/?page_id=189', 0, 'page', '', 0),
