the <a href="https://docs.nexmo.com/messaging/us-short-codes-api/event-based-alerts/send-event-based-alerts/api-reference#delivery_receipt">delivery receipt</a> at your <a href="https://docs.nexmo.com/messaging/setup-callbacks">webhook endpoint</a> so you can see:\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>If the <a href="https://docs.nexmo.com/messaging/us-short-codes-api/event-based-alerts/send-event-based-alerts/api-reference#dlr_status">status</a> was <i>delivered</i>.</li>\r\n 	<li>When and how the message was made.</li>\r\n 	<li>How much the message cost.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<ul class="nav nav-tabs">\r\n 	<li class="active"><a href="https://docs.nexmo.com/messaging/us-short-codes-api/event-based-alerts/send-event-based-alerts#rpphp" data-toggle="tab">PHP</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href="https://docs.nexmo.com/messaging/us-short-codes-api/event-based-alerts/send-event-based-alerts#rppython" data-toggle="tab">Python</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href="https://docs.nexmo.com/messaging/us-short-codes-api/event-based-alerts/send-event-based-alerts#rpruby" data-toggle="tab">Ruby</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href="https://docs.nexmo.com/messaging/us-short-codes-api/event-based-alerts/send-event-based-alerts#rpnodejs" data-toggle="tab">Node.js</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class="tab-content">\r\n<div id="rpphp" class="tab-pane fade in active"><i id="rp_php_button" class="fa fa-files-o copy-img" data-clipboard-action="copy" data-clipboard-target="#rp_php"></i>\r\n<pre id="rp_php" class="highlight"><code class="php hljs" data-lang="php"><span class="hljs-meta">&lt;?php</span>\r\n<span class="hljs-comment">// work with get or post</span>\r\n$request = array_merge($_GET, $_POST);\r\n\r\n<span class="hljs-comment">// Check that this is a delivery receipt.</span>\r\n<span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (!<span class="hljs-keyword">isset</span>($request[<span class="hljs-string">''messageId''</span>]) <span class="hljs-keyword">OR</span> !<span class="hljs-keyword">isset</span>($request[<span class="hljs-string">''status''</span>])) {\r\n    error_log(<span class="hljs-string">''This is not a delivery receipt''</span>);\r\n    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;\r\n}\r\n\r\n<span class="hljs-comment">//Check if your message has been delivered correctly.</span>\r\n<span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> ($request[<span class="hljs-string">''status''</span>] == <span class="hljs-string">''delivered''</span>) {\r\n    error_log(<span class="hljs-string">"Your message to {$request[''msisdn'']} (message id {$request[''messageId'']}) was delivered."</span>);\r\n    error_log(<span class="hljs-string">"The cost was {$request[''price'']}."</span>);\r\n} <span class="hljs-keyword">elseif</span> ($request[<span class="hljs-string">''status''</span>] != <span class="hljs-string">''accepted''</span>) {\r\n    error_log(<span class="hljs-string">"Your message to {$request[''msisdn'']} (message id {$request[''messageId'']}) was accepted by the carrier."</span>);\r\n    error_log(<span class="hljs-string">"The cost was {$request[''price'']}."</span>);\r\n} <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> {\r\n    error_log(<span class="hljs-string">"Your message to {$request[''msisdn'']} has a status of: {$request[''status'']}."</span>);\r\n    error_log(<span class="hljs-string">"Check err-code {$request[''err-code'']} against the documentation."</span>);\r\n}\r\n</code></pre>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<strong>Note</strong>: remember to send return <em>200 ok</em> when you receive the delivery receipt.', 'Sending Alerts', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'sending-alerts', '', '', '2017-05-09 06:50:20', '2017-05-09 06:50:20', '', 195, 'http://localhost:8080/Nexmo/Source/BE/?page_id=199', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(200, 1, '2017-05-09 06:50:20', '2017-05-09 06:50:20', 'You use Event Based Alerts to send custom messages to your users. Before you use this API you have to <a href="https://docs.nexmo.com/tools/dashboard#event_based_alerts">Setup a Pre-approved Short Code for Event Based Alerts</a>\r\n\r\nThe workflow for sending Event Based Alerts is:\r\n<figure><img src="https://docs.nexmo.com/assets/images/workflow_sending_event_based_alerts.svg" alt="workflow_sending_event_based_alerts" /></figure>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Send an Event Based Alerts <a href="https://docs.nexmo.com/messaging/us-short-codes-api/event-based-alerts/send-event-based-alerts/api-reference#request">request</a>.</li>\r\n 	<li>Check the <a href="https://docs.nexmo.com/messaging/us-short-codes-api/event-based-alerts/send-event-based-alerts/api-reference#status-codes">response codes</a> in the <a href="https://docs.nexmo.com/messaging/us-short-codes-api/event-based-alerts/send-event-based-alerts/api-reference#response">response</a> and ensure that you sent the request to Nexmo correctly.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nexmo sends the alert to your user.</li>\r\n 	<li>Receive the <a href="https://docs.nexmo.com/messaging/us-short-codes-api/two-factor-authentication/api-reference#delivery-receipt">delivery receipt</a> at your <a href="https://docs.nexmo.com/messaging/setup-callbacks">webhook endpoint</a> and verify delivery.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h2>Implementing the Event Based Alerts workflow</h2>\r\nTo send Event Based Alerts to your users:\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Send an Event Based Alerts <a href="https://docs.nexmo.com/messaging/us-short-codes-api/event-based-alerts/send-event-based-alerts/api-reference#request">request</a>. If you have multiple templates, remember to set the <i>template</i> number in your request.\r\n<ul class="nav nav-tabs">\r\n 	<li class="active"><a href="https://docs.nexmo.com/messaging/us-short-codes-api/event-based-alerts/send-event-based-alerts#php" data-toggle="tab">PHP</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href="https://docs.nexmo.com/messaging/us-short-codes-api/event-based-alerts/send-event-based-alerts#python" data-toggle="tab">Python</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href="https://docs.nexmo.com/messaging/us-short-codes-api/event-based-alerts/send-event-based-alerts#ruby" data-toggle="tab">Ruby</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href="https://docs.nexmo.com/messaging/us-short-codes-api/event-based-alerts/send-event-based-alerts#nodejs" data-toggle="tab">Node.js</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class="tab-content">\r\n<div id="php" class="tab-pane fade in active"><i id="request_php_button" class="fa fa-files-o copy-img" data-clipboard-action="copy" data-clipboard-target="#request_php"></i>\r\n<pre id="request_php" class="highlight"><code class="php hljs" data-lang="php"><span class="hljs-meta">&lt;?php</span>\r\n$url = <span class="hljs-string">''https://rest.nexmo.com/sc/us/alert/json?''</span> . http_build_query([\r\n        <span class="hljs-string">''api_key''</span> =&gt; <span class="hljs-string">''API_KEY''</span>,\r\n        <span class="hljs-string">''api_secret''</span> =&gt; <span class="hljs-string">''API_SECRET''</span>,\r\n        <span class="hljs-string">''to''</span> =&gt; <span class="hljs-string">''441632960960''</span>,\r\n        <span class="hljs-string">''TEMPLATE_VARIABLE_NAME''</span> =&gt; <span class="hljs-string">''VALUE''</span>\r\n    ]);\r\n$ch = curl_init($url);\r\ncurl_setopt($ch, CURLOPT_RETURNTRANSFER, <span class="hljs-keyword">true</span>);\r\n$response = curl_exec($ch);\r\n</code></pre>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></li>\r\n 	<li>Check the <a href="https://docs.nexmo.com/messaging/us-short-codes-api/event-based-alerts/send-event-based-alerts/api-reference#status-codes">response codes</a> in the <a href="https://docs.nexmo.com/messaging/us-short-codes-api/event-based-alerts/send-event-based-alerts/api-reference#response">response</a> and ensure that you sent the request to Nexmo correctly:\r\n<ul class="nav nav-tabs">\r\n 	<li class="active"><a href="https://docs.nexmo.com/messaging/us-short-codes-api/event-based-alerts/send-event-based-alerts#rspphp" data-toggle="tab">PHP</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href="https://docs.nexmo.com/messaging/us-short-codes-api/event-based-alerts/send-event-based-alerts#rsppython" data-toggle="tab">Python</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href="https://docs.nexmo.com/messaging/us-short-codes-api/event-based-alerts/send-event-based-alerts#rspruby" data-toggle="tab">Ruby</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href="https://docs.nexmo.com/messaging/us-short-codes-api/event-based-alerts/send-event-based-alerts#rspnodejs" data-toggle="tab">Node.js</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class="tab-content">\r\n<div id="rspphp" class="tab-pane fade in active"><i id="response_php_button" class="fa fa-files-o copy-img" data-clipboard-action="copy" data-clipboard-target="#response_php"></i>\r\n<pre id="response_php" class="highlight"><code class="php hljs" data-lang="php"><span class="hljs-meta">&lt;?php</span>\r\n<span class="hljs-comment">//Decode the json object you retrieved when you ran the request.</span>\r\n$decoded_response = json_decode($response, <span class="hljs-keyword">true</span>);\r\nerror_log(<span class="hljs-string">''You sent ''</span> . $decoded_response[<span class="hljs-string">''message-count''</span>] . <span class="hljs-string">'' messages.''</span>);\r\n\r\n<span class="hljs-keyword">foreach</span> ( $decoded_response[<span class="hljs-string">''messages''</span>] <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> $message ) {\r\n    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> ($message[<span class="hljs-string">''status''</span>] == <span class="hljs-number">0</span>) {\r\n        error_log(<span class="hljs-string">"Success "</span> . $message[<span class="hljs-string">''message-id''</span>]);\r\n    } <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> {\r\n        error_log(<span class="hljs-string">"Error {$message[''status'']} {$message[''error-text'']}"</span>);\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n</code></pre>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></li>\r\n 	<li>Nexmo sends the alert to your user.</li>\r\n 	<li>Receive the <a href="https://docs.nexmo.com/messaging/us-short-codes-api/event-based-alerts/send-event-based-alerts/api-reference#delivery_receipt">delivery receipt</a> at your <a href="https://docs.nexmo.com/messaging/setup-callbacks">webhook endpoint</a> so you can see:\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>If the <a href="https://docs.nexmo.com/messaging/us-short-codes-api/event-based-alerts/send-event-based-alerts/api-reference#dlr_status">status</a> was <i>delivered</i>.</li>\r\n 	<li>When and how the message was made.</li>\r\n 	<li>How much the message cost.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<ul class="nav nav-tabs">\r\n 	<li class="active"><a href="https://docs.nexmo.com/messaging/us-short-codes-api/event-based-alerts/send-event-based-alerts#rpphp" data-toggle="tab">PHP</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href="https://docs.nexmo.com/messaging/us-short-codes-api/event-based-alerts/send-event-based-alerts#rppython" data-toggle="tab">Python</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href="https://docs.nexmo.com/messaging/us-short-codes-api/event-based-alerts/send-event-based-alerts#rpruby" data-toggle="tab">Ruby</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href="https://docs.nexmo.com/messaging/us-short-codes-api/event-based-alerts/send-event-based-alerts#rpnodejs" data-toggle="tab">Node.js</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class="tab-content">\r\n<div id="rpphp" class="tab-pane fade in active"><i id="rp_php_button" class="fa fa-files-o copy-img" data-clipboard-action="copy" data-clipboard-target="#rp_php"></i>\r\n<pre id="rp_php" class="highlight"><code class="php hljs" data-lang="php"><span class="hljs-meta">&lt;?php</span>\r\n<span class="hljs-comment">// work with get or post</span>\r\n$request = array_merge($_GET, $_POST);\r\n\r\n<span class="hljs-comment">// Check that this is a delivery receipt.</span>\r\n<span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (!<span class="hljs-keyword">isset</span>($request[<span class="hljs-string">''messageId''</span>]) <span class="hljs-keyword">OR</span> !<span class="hljs-keyword">isset</span>($request[<span class="hljs-string">''status''</span>])) {\r\n    error_log(<span class="hljs-string">''This is not a delivery receipt''</span>);\r\n    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;\r\n}\r\n\r\n<span class="hljs-comment">//Check if your message has been delivered correctly.</span>\r\n<span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> ($request[<span class="hljs-string">''status''</span>] == <span class="hljs-string">''delivered''</span>) {\r\n    error_log(<span class="hljs-string">"Your message to {$request[''msisdn'']} (message id {$request[''messageId'']}) was delivered."</span>);\r\n    error_log(<span class="hljs-string">"The cost was {$request[''price'']}."</span>);\r\n} <span class="hljs-keyword">elseif</span> ($request[<span class="hljs-string">''status''</span>] != <span class="hljs-string">''accepted''</span>) {\r\n    error_log(<span class="hljs-string">"Your message to {$request[''msisdn'']} (message id {$request[''messageId'']}) was accepted by the carrier."</span>);\r\n    error_log(<span class="hljs-string">"The cost was {$request[''price'']}."</span>);\r\n} <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> {\r\n    error_log(<span class="hljs-string">"Your message to {$request[''msisdn'']} has a status of: {$request[''status'']}."</span>);\r\n    error_log(<span class="hljs-string">"Check err-code {$request[''err-code'']} against the documentation."</span>);\r\n}\r\n</code></pre>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<strong>Note</strong>: remember to send return <em>200 ok</em> when you receive the delivery receipt.', 'Sending Alerts', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '199-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-05-09 06:50:20', '2017-05-09 06:50:20', '', 199, 'http://localhost:8080/Nexmo/Source/BE/199-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
